  <evidence rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Our Web site includes social media features including the Facebook Like button and widgets such as the Share this button or other interactive mini-programs that run on our site the Social Media Features These features may collect your IP address which page you are visiting on our site and may set a cookie to enable the feature to function properly Social Media Features are either hosted by a third party or hosted directly us Your interactions with these Social Media Features are governed by the privacy policy of the company providing it</evidence>
</owl:NamedIndividual>

