  <evidence rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">We may disclose personal information in some other limited circumstances but we will specifically describe them to you when we collect the information such as in the rules of a contest or a new service For example if we are going to give personal information to a contest s sponsor we will disclose it when you sign up for the contest so that you can decide whether to enter</evidence>
